        </processinfo>
        <relatedmaterial id="ref33">
            <head>Related Archival Materials note</head>
            <p>The Archives of American Art holds an oral history interview with Elsie Driggs conducted by Francine Tyler October 30-December 5, 1985.</p>
        </relatedmaterial>
